29:00.256 --> 29:03.705
¢Ü Lord, lord ¢Ü

29:03.705 --> 29:07.319
¢Ü hammer will be the death of me, yes! ¢Ü

29:10.987 --> 29:15.449
Well...
Okay, okay then. Thank you.

29:15.449 --> 29:17.929
Adrian, the point is
that he was a steel driver.

29:17.929 --> 29:23.405
There was a big contest between John Henry
and the big, new, modern steam drill,

29:23.405 --> 29:26.370
and John Henry won.

29:26.370 --> 29:27.976
- He, he did?
- He won, yes.

29:27.976 --> 29:30.196
I mean, absolutely.
That's why I'm telling you this.

29:30.196 --> 29:32.406
Oh...
yeah.

29:32.406 --> 29:37.035
He won, he was a hero.
Everybody loved him.

29:37.035 --> 29:40.345
God, I just loved it when everybody
