¢Ü laid down his hammer and he died ¢Ü

29:50.823 --> 29:54.445
¢Ü lord, lord ¢Ü

29:54.445 --> 29:58.814
¢Ü he laid down his hammer ¢Ü

29:58.814 --> 30:02.954
¢Ü and he died ¢Ü

30:06.727 --> 30:09.961
So he...
he died?

30:09.961 --> 30:12.885
Oh.

30:12.885 --> 30:14.918
Yeah, I guess he did.

30:14.918 --> 30:18.466
No, no, no, in this version. You know,
there were a lot of versions.

30:18.466 --> 30:21.121
- I think our time is up.
- No, no, no, it's not, Adrian.

30:21.121 --> 30:23.288
- Yeah, I think our time is up.
- No, it's only 20 after.

30:23.288 --> 30:26.353
Adrian, no, really. Ad, Adri...

30:27.315 --> 30:30.550
This body's pretty badly mutilated.
We're gonna need a little more time.

30:30.550 --> 30:33.959
We don't have any more time, doctor.
What the hell have you been doing?

30:33.959 --> 30:36.281
We've been working 24/7
on this case like you told us.

30:36.281 --> 30:39.040
Okay, all right.
Here's my best guess.

30:39.040 --> 30:42.210
The victim was hit first,
but the blow didn't kill him.

30:42.210 --> 30:44.548
Cause of death was probably suffocation.

30:44.548 --> 30:46.680
The other injuries were inflicted postmortem.

30:46.680 --> 30:50.194
Keep going, keep working.
Call me back when you're sure.

30:50.194 --> 30:51.557
Cause of death, suffocation.

30:51.557 --> 30:54.920
Let's add that to the psychological profile.

30:54.920 --> 30:57.161
You're wrong about Adrian Monk.

30:57.161 --> 30:58.983
- Am I?
- Yep.

30:58.983 --> 31:03.552
I know he's a little strange
and he can be difficult but,

31:03.552 --> 31:07.170
I can tell you of at least 12 different cases
where all of the evidence...

31:07.170 --> 31:09.122
Captain Stottlemeyer...

31:09.122 --> 31:12.546
you're looking at $1/2
billion worth of equipment.

31:12.546 --> 31:17.316
Are you trying to tell me that your funny
little friend is smarter than all of this?

31:18.709 --> 31:20.814
Yes, I am.

31:23.529 --> 31:27.855
Is that a radar detector? / No.

31:27.855 --> 31:29.360
You wouldn't tell me
if it was, would you?

31:29.360 --> 31:31.992
It's not a radar detector.

31:33.157 --> 31:34.767
Right.

31:34.767 --> 31:36.297
Here's an updated profile.

31:36.297 --> 31:38.575
Suffocation indicates
the assault was personal,

31:38.575 --> 31:40.852
motivated by repressed anger.

31:40.852 --> 31:43.560
Choice of street performer
as victim may be significant.

31:43.560 --> 31:47.561
The suspect's father
was probably a failed musician.

31:47.561 --> 31:50.075
- So he hates street musicians.
- Who doesn't?

31:50.075 --> 31:51.755
We can nail this bastard.
Sweep the city.

31:51.755 --> 31:55.911
I want all musicians off the street,
except one.

32:03.435 --> 32:05.318
5, 6, 7, 8...

32:05.318 --> 32:09.431
¢Ü Well, I'm tired of sucking up
