32:11.974 --> 32:13.730
Bravo two, locked and loaded.

32:13.730 --> 32:17.226
¢Ü Cuff my brothers and sisters
oh, that's not the way to be ¢Ü

32:17.226 --> 32:24.537
¢Ü 'cause, baby, those days are gone
