32:44.874 --> 32:46.173
Well, that was the captain.

32:46.173 --> 32:49.092
They're all at the Sheridan square
trying to stake it out.

32:49.092 --> 32:52.126
- Want to go check it out?
- Nah, I'd just be in the way.

32:52.126 --> 32:54.450
Here's where I belong. In there.

32:54.450 --> 32:57.687
Why don't you call Dr. Walsh?
Tell him to meet me here.

32:57.687 --> 33:01.261
He can stuff me and put me on
display with all the other relics.

33:01.261 --> 33:04.445
Come on, Mr. Monk. You know the
medical examiner's a little busy today.

33:04.445 --> 33:07.282
Everybody's working on the big case.

33:08.054 --> 33:10.757
What?

33:10.757 --> 33:13.275
- What did you say?
- I said they're too busy.

33:13.275 --> 33:16.935
They're all working on
the Six-Way killer thing.

33:16.935 --> 33:19.466
That's right.

33:19.466 --> 33:21.795
Natalie, you're right!

33:21.795 --> 33:26.816
That's the key!
Everybody is too busy.

33:26.816 --> 33:29.241
- What time is it?
- It's 12:45.

33:29.241 --> 33:31.095
15 minutes, we gotta hurry.
Come on!

33:31.095 --> 33:33.911
- What's going on?
- I'll tell you in the car. Let's go!

33:37.942 --> 33:41.556
¢Ü I don't need a captain
