35:51.075 --> 35:52.609
You got, like, 5 bucks in there.

35:52.609 --> 35:54.322
- Really?
- Yeah.

35:56.602 --> 35:59.277
What the hell's going on?
Who told you to stop?

35:59.277 --> 36:01.674
I did. / What are you doing?

36:01.674 --> 36:03.488
I told you before.
She doesn't matter.

36:03.488 --> 36:06.315
Actually, agent Thorpe,
she not only matters,

36:06.315 --> 36:08.608
she is the key to this whole case.

36:08.608 --> 36:11.958
Your so-called Six-Way killer
killed her first.

36:11.958 --> 36:14.654
The other kid, the street musician,
was just a diversion.

36:14.654 --> 36:18.829
It's true.
Captain, the same guy killed both.

36:19.804 --> 36:22.109
You found a liquor bottle
in the killer's car.

36:22.109 --> 36:26.238
Remember, there was a cognac stain
on her sleeve.

36:26.238 --> 36:31.247
Monk.
Do you know who did it?

36:31.247 --> 36:33.331
She'll tell us if it's not too late.

36:33.331 --> 36:35.368
We've already wasted a day and a half.

36:35.368 --> 36:40.483
It was the deadline, 36 hours.
It seemed so arbitrary, didn't it?

36:40.483 --> 36:45.218
