how hard everybody was working

36:48.966 --> 36:51.888
on the Six-Way killer case.
And I wondered,

36:51.888 --> 36:56.624
"who would benefit from that?"
And there's only one answer.

36:56.624 --> 37:00.367
The man who killed this woman.

37:00.367 --> 37:05.137
Here's what happened. Ms. Garnett
met a doctor at the convention.

37:05.137 --> 37:08.341
He took her out to dinner.

37:08.341 --> 37:12.644
I don't know what they ordered,
but it must've been pretty special.

37:12.644 --> 37:14.844
- Why do you say that?
- Bcause whatever it was,

37:14.844 --> 37:17.652
it could've been traced
back to that restaurant.

37:17.652 --> 37:23.022
That meal, what they ate, that's
what this whole case has been about.

37:23.022 --> 37:25.345
He must've paid for it with a credit card.

37:25.345 --> 37:28.663
Something that we could trace later.

37:28.663 --> 37:31.058
Just listen.

37:31.058 --> 37:35.753
They ended up at Mt. Davidson park.
Something went wrong.

37:35.753 --> 37:39.187
We'll never know exactly what happened.
All we know is that she got away.

37:39.187 --> 37:42.459
She ran across the street
to the gas station.

37:42.459 --> 37:45.466
