37:50.874 --> 37:55.666
But he also knew
that if he could stall us, distract us,

37:55.666 --> 38:00.145
eventually the food
in her stomach would be digested.

38:00.145 --> 38:03.985
And the evidence would
be gone. / 36 hours.

38:03.985 --> 38:07.817
Exactly. Everything's gone in
a day and a half, even after death.

38:07.817 --> 38:09.187
So he distracted us.

38:09.187 --> 38:12.182
He picked a victim at random,
a street performer.

38:12.182 --> 38:14.495
And he killed him
in a particularly gruesome way.

38:14.495 --> 38:17.008
Six particularly gruesome ways, actually.

38:17.008 --> 38:20.101
